## âš™ï¸ How It Works
1. A random number is generated using `Math.random()` :contentReference[oaicite:0]{index=0}
2. User inputs a guess between 1 and 30
3. Attempts decrease after each guess
4. Feedback is displayed dynamically
5. Player can restart the game without refreshing the page

## â–¶ï¸ How to Play
Open `index.html` in your browser.  
Enter a number and click **Guess!**

